biotools.summary: Solyntus, the New Highly Contiguous Reference Genome for Potato (Solanum tuberosum). Solyntus genome sequence consortium. Genome sequence of the diploid potato cultivar Solyntus. A growing collection of datasets, data-mining tools (under development) and genetic resources for the highly homozygous, relatively vigorous and self-compatible potato genotype Solyntus.
